## ⚙️ How It Works

1. GitHub detects a **push / schedule / manual trigger**
2. GitHub Actions starts the workflow
3. Python environment is prepared
4. Tamanna AI Head runs automatically
5. New files are committed & pushed back
6. System stays online 24/7 ⚡

